headline: Up More Than 200% in the Past 5 Years, Can Costco Continue Its Momentum in 2025?
summary: Costco (NASDAQ: COST) is one of the best-performing large-cap retail stocks over the past five years.  It continued to show why it's one of the top retailers when it once again reported strong results for its fiscal first quarter.  This was the first quarterly report since Costco implemented a membership fee hike that went into effect in September.
